\s TURI KU RUGAMBA RWANYUMA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Turi ku rugamba rwa nyuma, n’\bd*\bd I\bd*\bd jambo ry’Imana, riduhanura yuko, twokwizera \bd*\bd Uwanesheje \bd*\bd ./.Niho natwe tuzoshobora kunesha./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Aho niho har’\bdit*\bdit A\bdit*\bdit gakiza k’Imana, n’ukwambar’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ibirwanishwa vyose, mu gusengera muri Mpwemu, no mu kwitwaza inkota ya Mpwemu, ari\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ryo Jambo ry’Uhoraho.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Kw’\bd*\bd I\bd*\bd jambo ry’Imana, rivuga riti ic’umuntu abiba, nico azokwimbura, none natwe ni tubibe muri Mpwemu\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Tuze twimbure \bd*\bd Ubugingo \bd*\bd budashira./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Aho niho har’Agakiza k’Imana, n’ukwambar’ ibirwanishwa vyose, mu gusengera muri Mpwemu, no mu kwitwaza inkota ya Mpwemu, ari ryo Jambo ry’Uhoraho.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ntituzoshobozwa n’inkomezi zacu, kiretse ni twizera Umwami Yesu, niho tuzorongorwa, na Mpwemu Yera\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Tukagendera no mu muco w’\bd*\bd I\bd*\bd jambo./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Aho niho har’Agakiza k’Imana, n’ukwambar’ ibirwanishwa vyose, mu gusengera muri Mpwemu, no mu kwitwaza inkota ya Mpwemu, ari ryo Jambo ry’Uhoraho.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ijambo ry’Imana, ni ryo rizoduha kugira ingeso nziza, hamwe n’ubwenge, ukwirinda n’ukwihangana navyo\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Bituj’imbere mu rugendo rwacu./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Aho niho har’Agakiza k’Imana, n’ukwambar’ ibirwanishwa vyose, mu gusengera muri Mpwemu, no mu kwitwaza inkota ya Mpwemu, ari ryo Jambo ry’Uhoraho.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ni twubaha ijambo ry’Imana vy’ukuri, kandi tugakunda na bene Data, niho tuzogira intsinzi muri vyose\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.N’Imana izoshimagizwa muri twe./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Aho niho har’Agakiza k’Imana, n’ukwambar’ ibirwanishwa vyose, mu gusengera muri Mpwemu, no mu kwitwaza inkota ya Mpwemu, ari ryo Jambo ry’Uhoraho.\bdit*
